snippet.title: Wayward Strand Gameplay Sneak Peek - Coming September 15th!
snippet.description:
The video description has been updated 07-07-22 to reflect the new release date, despite the video itself quoting the old launch date :) thanks!

Wayward Strand will be landing on Nintendo Switch, PlayStation 5, PlayStation 4, Xbox Series X|S, Xbox One X, and Windows on September 15, 2022.

This is a sneak peek of some of Wayward Strand's gameplay that we put together a couple of months ago - we're excited to share more of the game soon!
